analysisPopulations.name: Full Analysis Set
analysisPopulations.text: The Full Analysis Set (FAS) includes all subjects randomized to the study. Subjects will be analyzed according to the treatment group to which they were randomized.
analysisPopulations.label: FAS
analysisPopulations.populationDescription: The Full Analysis Set (FAS) includes all subjects randomized to the study. Subjects will be analyzed according to the treatment group to which they were randomized.

analysisPopulations.name: Safety Analysis Set
analysisPopulations.text: The Safety Analysis Set includes all subjects who received at least one dose of study treatment (axicabtagene ciloleucel or SOC). Subjects will be analyzed according to the treatment they actually received.
analysisPopulations.label: SAF
analysisPopulations.populationDescription: The Safety Analysis Set includes all subjects who received at least one dose of study treatment (axicabtagene ciloleucel or SOC). Subjects will be analyzed according to the treatment they actually received.
analysisPopulations.criteria: Received at least one dose of study treatment

analysisPopulations.name: Safety Analysis Set - ASCT
analysisPopulations.text: The Safety Analysis Set - ASCT includes all subjects in the SOC arm who received high-dose therapy (HDT) and autologous stem cell transplant (ASCT).
analysisPopulations.label: SAF-ASCT
analysisPopulations.populationDescription: The Safety Analysis Set - ASCT includes all subjects in the SOC arm who received high-dose therapy (HDT) and autologous stem cell transplant (ASCT).
analysisPopulations.criteria: Randomized to SOC arm AND received HDT and ASCT

analysisPopulations.name: QoL Analysis Set
analysisPopulations.text: The QoL Analysis Set includes all subjects in the FAS who have a baseline and at least one post-baseline QoL assessment.
analysisPopulations.label: QoL Set
analysisPopulations.populationDescription: The QoL Analysis Set includes all subjects in the FAS who have a baseline and at least one post-baseline QoL assessment.
analysisPopulations.criteria: Randomized AND has baseline QoL assessment AND has >=1 post-baseline QoL assessment

analysisPopulations.name: Retreatment Analysis Sets
analysisPopulations.text: The Retreatment Analysis Sets include all subjects who receive a second course of axicabtagene ciloleucel treatment.
analysisPopulations.label: Retreatment Set
analysisPopulations.populationDescription: The Retreatment Analysis Sets include all subjects who receive a second course of axicabtagene ciloleucel treatment.
analysisPopulations.criteria: Received second course of axicabtagene ciloleucel

characteristics.name: Response to first-line therapy
characteristics.description: Primary refractory versus relapse ≤ 6 months versus relapse > 6 and ≤ 12 months

characteristics.name: Second-line age-adjusted IPI
characteristics.description: International Prognostic Index (0 to 1 versus 2 to 3) at time of screening
